Are you a Data Scientist with experience, eager of challenges, ready for a new adventure?

We are BID, a fast-growing consultancy startup specialized in Advanced Analytics & Artificial Intelligence. We are a team of specialists passionate about technology and innovation applied to the field of Data Analysis. Our mission is to provide excellent consulting services to our cross industry customers across Europe, interpreting business needs and finding the right technological solution. Our main strength lies in the Analytics world, with a specific focus on CRM, Risk Management and Innovation Technology.




Who are we seeking?

You have a degree in Statistics, Economics, Math or related field, with a minimum of 2 - 4 years of professionale experience;
You have broad experience across Analytical Platforms using predictive models with advanced machine learning algorithms;
You have validated expertise in one or more of the following topics: Data Mining, Forecasting, Optimization, Text Analytics, Artificial Intelligence;
You can communicate with people of various technical and business backgrounds, explaining difficult technical concepts in simple terms to business users.




What will you do?

Processing and analyzing large volumes of (customer) data;
Building predictive and machine learning models with algorithms such as Neural Networks, Decision Trees, Boosting/Ensemble methods, Clustering, etc.;
Interacting with customers from the data analysis stage to the final report presentation;
Constantly innovating by crafting new variables; improving modeling techniques to boost model performance; maintaining and refining the processes and procedures for building high-end analytic modeling solutions;
Writing coherent reports and making presentations on high-end analytical projects;
Implementing innovative techniques, such as text analytics and deep learning.




What do we offer?

You will be part of a multidisciplinary group, with experienced people that will help you through your professional path;
You will experience a personal growth, learning from different topics and areas;
You will have the opportunity to work on exciting and creative projects, crossing different industries;
You will work in a startup environment, with attention to work-life balance and possibility of smart working.




The job is located in Milan.

We are an equal opportunity employer and value diversity at our company. We do not discriminate on the basis of race, religion, color, national origin, gender, sexual orientation, age, marital status, veteran status, or disability status.

BID processes your personal data in compliance with the GDPR legislation. By applying for the job offer, you declare that you have read the privacy policy --> https://goo.gl/xUBmzB

